# Sales Performance Analysis Dashboard
The dashboard was originally developed as part of a university project and is presented in Polish. All project documentation and analysis are provided in English.

## Project Overview

This project presents an interactive sales analysis dashboard developed in Microsoft Power BI. The report enables users to analyze sales performance across different countries, products, and time periods through interactive visualizations.

## Objectives

- Analyze sales performance over time.
- Compare sales across countries.
- Identify best-performing products.
- Explore sales distribution using interactive filters.
- Support business decision-making through data visualization.

## Technologies

- Microsoft Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX
- Microsoft Excel

## Dashboard Features

- Monthly sales trend analysis
- Sales by product
- Sales by country
- Interactive map visualization
- Country filtering
- Product comparison

